# Notes for generators and validators
# --------------------
# - A generator may produce initial Summary/Details/Example/Links content,
#   but the "Historical" field should be reviewed by a human to ensure accuracy.
# - Validators should:
#   * Assert header coverage: headers == EnumSet.allOf(JavaFeature.class)
#   * Assert required sections exist and are in order per block
#   * Fail on duplicate headers or empty example code blocks
#   * Fail if any bare URL is present or non at all (every features needs a link)
#   * Optionally check link reachability with a short timeout, store reachable links in file; make this optional for CI via a flag
# - Keep blocks small and focused: prefer short examples and 2-4 paragraph details.

